

NOTE: In case of faulty release, remember to remove the release *tag* as well. 

1: Compilation with max. warning level (pass with no warning)
2: All tests must pass 
3: Update file NEWS 
4: Update file DESCRIPTION
5: Check scripts/functions in directory examples/  
6: Commit and make molsim release
7: Check install release from http address (remove path to local repository first)
8: Generate sha 
  - >> urlwrite ("https://github.com/jesperschmidthansen/molsim/archive/refs/tags/v<version>.tar.gz", "molsim-<version>.tar.gz");
  - >> hash ("sha256", fileread ("molsim-<version>.tar.gz"))
9a: Use gnu-octave/package link and open molsim.yaml
9b: Edit molsim.yaml as necessary and 
    propose changes + 
	create pull request + 
	merge pull request + 
	merge + 
	confirm merge

